Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,水善\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,土强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,火烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,气和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Air.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前,这四大国和谐共处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Long ago, the four nations lived together in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,然而,火国发起的战争结束了和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Then everything changed when the Fire Nation attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只有同时掌握四种元素的降世神通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Only the Avatar, master of all four elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,才能结束战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}could stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然而在大家最需要他的时候,他却消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}But when the world needed him most, he vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,100年后,我和哥哥发现了新的降世神通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}100 years passed, and my brother and I discovered the new Avatar,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个御气师,名叫安昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}an airbender named Aang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管他的御气术着实厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}And although his airbending skills are great,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但在拯救苍生之前,他要学的还有很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}he has a lot to learn before he's ready to save anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,呃!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Unh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我坚信安昂能拯救这个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}But I believe Aang can save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:44.50,标题,,0,0,0,,降世神通 最后的气宗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:53.55,标题,,0,0,210,,第一卷 水 第十二回 风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你,安昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We need you, Aang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我也需要你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I need you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小心啊,伙计们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Be careful, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都去哪了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉措大师?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Gyatso?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不辞而别?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Why did you disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你,安昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We need you, Aang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aaaaah!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你,安昂, 我们需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We need you, Aang. We need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你,安昂, 我们需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We need you, Aang. We need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Huh! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:01:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又被抓了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Did we get captured again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事,我做了一个噩梦而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}It's nothing. I just had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,继续睡吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪,我都被你弄醒两次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You don't have to tell me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧,安昂?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Are you all right, Aang?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我还好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近好像老做噩梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You seem to be having a lot of nightmares lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,想不想跟我谈谈?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You want to tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的,我想我只是需要多休息休息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Ithinkijust need some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想不想知道我梦到了什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You guys want to hear about my dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没事,一般人我还不告诉他呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}That's okay. I didn't want to talk about it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们快看,天气多好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Look at those clear skies, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这种天气飞行再好不过啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Should be some smooth flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们最好赶快飞去市场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Well, we'd better smoothly fly ourselves to a market,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们的食物都已经吃光了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}because we're out of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们等等,这正如我的梦一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Guys, wait. This was in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天不能去市场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We shouldn't go to the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你都梦见什么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}What happened in your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,食物会吃人啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Food eats people!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有,模模开口说人话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Also, Momo could talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你可说了一堆不友好的话哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You said some very unkind things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有一场暴风雨即将来临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}There is a storm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而且,来势不小啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}A big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你糊涂了吧,皇叔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You're out of your mind, uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:02:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,今天天气这么好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The weather is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,万里无云\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}There's not a cloud in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这场风暴从北方逼近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}A storm is approaching from the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议更改航线,向西南行驶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I suggest we alter our course and head southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道降世神通在向北行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We know the Avatar is traveling northward,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们也必须如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}so we will do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,祖寇殿下,你要考虑一下船员的安危\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Prince Zuko, consider the safety of the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,船员的安危无关紧要!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The safety of the crew doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,找到降世神通远比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Finding the Avatar is far more important
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人的安危都来得重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}than any individual's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请别误会,他只是一时头脑发热\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}He doesn't mean that. He's just all worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀,你听我说的准没错,这瓜简直完美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}It's good. It's perfect, I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我总觉得里面听起来稀里光趟的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I don't know if I like the sound of that swishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,稀里光趟的才好呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Swishing means it's ripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,说明瓜熟了,明白不?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}It's the ripe juices swishing around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没错的,卡塔拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I think it's true, Katara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,稀里光趟的就熟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Swishing means it's ripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚发现我们钱不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I just realized we're out of money, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喔...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,吃的没了,现在钱又花光了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Out of food and out of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在该怎么办啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Now what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以去打个工,聪明人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You could get a job, smart guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不该出海!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We shouldn't go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了,鱼哪天不能打啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Please! The fish can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今天将有大风暴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}There's going to be a terrible storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别说胡话!这么好的天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aw, you're crazy. It's a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没云、没风、没闪电的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}No clouds, no wind, no nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以别跟我唠叨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}so quit your nagging, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也许咱们该找个地方避一避\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Maybe we should find some shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑,避什么啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Are you kidding? Shelter from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的关节痛告诉我有一场暴风雨即将来临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}My joints say there's going to be a storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还是很大的一场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}a bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别拿你的关节跟我的脑子比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Well, it's your joints against my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那叫你的脑子找别人拖网吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Then I hope your brain can find someone else to haul that fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我是不会去的!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}‘cause I ain't coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就另找个新的渔夫!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Then I'll find a new fish hauler,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还付他双倍的工钱!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}and pay him double what you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这下你高兴了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}How do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你被雇了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You're hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦?你不是说要找份工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}What? You said get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他还付双倍工钱呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}And he's paying double.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,双倍工钱?你听谁胡诌的?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Double? Who told you that nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,呃!看来真让你的皇叔说着了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Oh. Looks like your uncle was right about the storm after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,侥幸猜中而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Lucky guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉,你最好学习一下如何尊敬别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Lieutenant, you'd better learn some respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我只能亲自教你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}or I will teach it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,说到尊敬,你懂什么叫尊敬吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}What do you know about respect?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧你对周围人说话的态度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The way you talk to everyone around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不论是为你辛苦工作的船员,还是你应当尊敬的皇叔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}from your hard-working crew to your esteemed uncle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本就不懂得什么叫尊敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}shows you know nothing about respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你只在乎你自己的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You don't care about anyone but yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,再说,我怎么能期望从一个被宠坏的王子那里得到尊敬呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Then again, what should I expect from a spoiled prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都冷静点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Easy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,够了!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是出海太久了,大家都累了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We're all a bit tired from being at sea so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信大家一块吃碗面条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm sure after a bowl of noodles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,能让每个人的心情都好一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}everyone will feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要你来维护我的船的秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I don't need your help keeping order on my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,索卡,你还是别出海了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Sokka, maybe this isn't such a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧,这都变天了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Look at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了这活我干定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I said I was gonna do this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不会因为什么坏天气就放弃的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I can't back out just because of some bad weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这个有纹身的小子还有点脑子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The boy with the tattoos has some sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该听他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You should listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,带纹身的小子?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Boy with tattoos?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是气和族的纹身吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Airbender tattoos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,活见鬼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Well, I'll be a hog monkey's uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你是降世神通,对吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You're the Avatar, ain't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如假包换\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别摆出那副笑脸!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Well, don't be so smiley about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,神通消失了近百年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The Avatar disappeared for a hundred years!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你背弃了这个世界!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You turned your back on the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,别冲他嚷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Don't yell at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,安昂从没有背弃任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aang would never turn his back on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,他没有吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Oh, he wouldn't, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那持续了百年的战争和痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Then I guess I must have imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我想像出来的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}the last hundred years of war and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,安昂是我见过的最勇敢的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aang is the bravest person I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我认识他以来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}He has done nothing but help people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直都在帮助他人,拯救生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}and save lives since I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当初消失并不是他的错,我说得没错吧,安昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}It's not his fault he disappeared, right, Aang?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,安昂,怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aang, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了,继续飞!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}That's right! Keep flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个老头真可恶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You're a horrible old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,阿柏,驾,驾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Appa, yip yip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Uhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,他们居然没说一声就走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Hey! They left without saying good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友怎么这么没礼貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Your friends ain't too polite, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不是嘛,你知道曾经吧...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I know. This one time, I was-Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,行了,别唠叨了,把这些拿舱里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}yeah, yeah. Get below deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉我跑掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm sorry for running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系,那个打渔的太过分了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}It's okay. That fisherman was way out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,其实他没说错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Actually, he wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这话怎么说?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在不想谈这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I don't want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟你这几天做的噩梦有关,对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}It has to do with your dream, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我说说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧,说来话长啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Well, it's kind of a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我去生火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm gonna try to get a little fire going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,长老们告诉我我就是降世神通那天,我终生难忘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'll never forget the day the monks told me I was the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,当时,我和其他的小孩在南墙外玩耍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I was playing with some other kids just outside the south wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在教他们如何玩「气轮球」\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I was trying to teach them how to do the air scooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,首先你得先把气凝成球状,然后快速骑上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}First you form a ball. Then you've got to get on quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,耶!哈哈哈!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Yeah! Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,喔吼!耶!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Whoo-hoo! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好的,让我试试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Okay, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快,骑上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Quick. Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 哇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Whoa. Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Uhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这个气轮球就像个陀螺一样,你得学会在上面保持平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You kind of have to balance on it like it's a top.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪,真是太难了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Man, that's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,安昂,你是在哪学会这招的?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Where did you learn that trick, Aang?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我自创的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I made it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哇!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,安昂,跟我们来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aang, come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有话要跟你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We need to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么知道会是我?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}How do you know it's me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们早就知道你是降世神通了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We have known you were the Avatar for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得这些东西吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Do you remember these?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是我小时候最喜爱的玩具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Those were some of my favorite toys when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,安昂,你从上千个玩具中单单选中了这几样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You chose them from among thousands of toys, Aang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你挑的这几样玩具是四位神通的遗物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The toys you picked were the four Avatar relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西属于神通前世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}These items belonged to Avatars past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是你的前世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Your own past lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我选它们,只是因为它们看上去很好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I just chose them because they seemed fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你选它们是因为你熟悉它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You chose them because they were familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一般来说我们会在你16岁后告诉你的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Normally, we would have told you of your identity when you turned 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然而天有不测风云\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}But there are troubling signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一场风暴即将来临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Storm clouds are gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕战争已经逼近这儿了,年轻的神通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I fear that war may be upon us, young Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你,安昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We need you, Aang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我听够他的命令了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm sick of taking his orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想再追什么神通了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}and I'm tired of chasing his Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,祖寇以为他自己是谁啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I mean, who does Zuko think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真的想知道吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Do you really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,艾洛将军,我们只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}General lroh, we were just--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我能加入你们吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}May I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以,长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,请试着去理解他吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Try to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我的侄子是个复杂的年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}my nephew is a complicated young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他经历的太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}He has been through much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让我进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,祖寇殿下,怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Prince Zuko, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想进军情室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I want to go into the war chamber,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是警卫不让我进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}but the guard won't let me pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我,里面没什么可看的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You're not missing anything. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这些会议无聊透顶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}These meetings are dreadfully boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果终有一天我将统治这个国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}If I'm going to rule this nation one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得我应该从现在开始尽可能地多学一些东西吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}don't you think I need to start learning as much as I can?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很好,但你得保证绝不开口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Very well, but you must promise not to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道这些老家伙们都有些敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}These old folks are a bit sensitive, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢您皇叔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Thank you, uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,土强国的抵抗力量都集中在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The Earth Kingdom defenses are concentrated here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一支由最强的御土师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}a dangerous battalion of their strongest earth benders,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,和最骁勇的战士们组成的危险队伍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}and fiercest warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我建议将第41师派往这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}So, I am recommending the 41st division.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是41师全都是由新兵组成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}But the 41st is entirely new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么可能击败这么强大的土强国军团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}How do you expect them to defeat a powerful Earth Kingdom battalion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不过是用来掩人耳目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}They'll be used as a distraction
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将从敌军的后防进攻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}while we mount an attack from the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,做诱饵,当然得用新鲜的肉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}What better to use as bait than fresh meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能就这样牺牲掉整个师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You can't sacrifice an entire division like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这些战士热爱并守护着我们的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Those soldiers love and defend our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能背叛他们?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}How can you betray them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,祖寇说得没错,不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Zuko was right, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这里他没有资格发言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}But it was not his place to speak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,于是接踵而来的是无法想像的恶果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}And there were dire consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以,发现自己是神通你感到很沮丧?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}So you were upset that you were the Avatar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该感到激动才对啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Why wouldn't you be excited about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道对此应该有什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Well, I didn't know how to feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道,在我得知这个消息之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}All I knew was that after I found out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都改变了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}everything began changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,不错啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Hey, not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都练过了是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You guys have been practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不光练习了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Not only that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还想出了一个用气轮球玩的游戏呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}we made up a game you can play with the air scooters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你是降世神通了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Now that you're the Avatar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把你分到哪一组\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}iVs kind of an unfair advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对其他组来说都是不公平的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}for whichever team you're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是,我还是我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}But I'm still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么,我不能玩了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}So, what? I can't play?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这样对大家才公平啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}That's the only fair way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了,安昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Sorry, Aang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好,哪队愿意让「金九」加入?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Okay, now, who wants to have Jinju on their team?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你这步下得很有意思啊,小神通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Very interesting move, young one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么说?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿!哈哈哈!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Hey! Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟然在这儿和他玩上了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You're playing games with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,神通现在需要加紧修炼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The Avatar should be training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,安昂今天已经练得够多的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aang has already trained enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,时间紧迫,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Time is short. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我得考考你对一些上层招式的理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I must test you on some high-level techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,只要我是他的监护人一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}No. As long as I am his guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我就有权决定他何时修炼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I will decide when he trains
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,以及何时在牌手棋盘上显丑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}And when he gets his butt kicked at Pai Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哼!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Hmmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,由于祖寇在那次会议上的失态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}After Zuko's outburst in the meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,火烈王震怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}the Fire Lord became very angry with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他说祖克殿下对将军的挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}He said that Prince Zuko's challenge of the general
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,完全是一种无礼的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}was an act of complete disrespect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而对于这种行为只有一种了结的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}And there was only one way to resolve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,火神祭——火功对决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Agni Kai. A fire duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:48.57,注释,,0,0,0,,Agni Kai, Agni是一个火神,Kai在日语中有集会的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,祖寇没把他得罪的老将军放在眼里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Zuko looked upon the old general he had insulted,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无畏惧地应战了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}and declared that he was not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是祖克误解了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}But Zuko misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,当他面对他的对手时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}When he turned to face his opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他诧异地发现对手并不是那个将军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}he was surprised to see it was not the general.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,祖克出言顶撞了将军的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Zuko had spoken out against the general's plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但他是在火烈国君的议战厅里讲出这些话的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}but by doing so in the Fire Lord's war room,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他无视的是火烈国之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}it was the Fire Lord whom he had disrespected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以祖克不得不跟他的生身父亲进行较量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Zuko would have to duel his own father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,当我刚刚感觉好点的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Then, just when I was starting to feel better,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,更糟的事发生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}something worse happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,安昂需要自由和快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aang needs to have freedom and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他理应像正常的孩子一样成长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}He needs to grow up as a normal boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哼!不管你怎样保护他,他终究要面对自己的命运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Hmm. You cannot keep protecting him from his destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉措,我知道你是好心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Gyatso, I know you mean well,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你对这孩子的关爱蒙蔽了你的判断力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}but you are letting your affection for the boy cloud your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想一心为他好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}All I want is what is best for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我们需要为天下人着想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}But what we need is what's best for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你和安昂必须分开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You and Aang must be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,神通将会被送去东气和寺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The Avatar will be sent away to the Eastern Air Temple
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,完成他的修炼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}to complete his training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那可真糟糕啊,安昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}That's awful, Aang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知该说些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么能这样对我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}How could they do that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们竟然要把我所了解的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}They wanted to take away everything I knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我所爱的人都从我身边带走!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}and everyone I loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!安昂,小心火炭!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Whoa! Hot cinders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起,我有点失态了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm sorry I got so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,长老们就这样把你送走是不对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You have a right to be angry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你有理由生气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}after the monks sent you away like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,其实,事情还没有发展到那步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Well, that's not exactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我既害怕又困惑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I was afraid and confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,安昂?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aang?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让他们把你从我身边带走的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm not going to let them take you away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,安昂?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aang?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,从那以后,我再也没有见过嘉措大师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I never saw Gyatso again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我只记得你们在冰川中发现了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Next thing I knew, I was waking up in your arms
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我在你的臂弯中醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}after you found me in the iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你出走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我出走后火宗的人袭击了我们寺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}And then the Fire Nation attacked our temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我的同胞们需要我,但我却不在那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}My people needed me, and I wasn't there to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道会...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You don't know what would have--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,世界需要我的时候,我也没能挺身而出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The world needed me, and I wasn't there to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-安昂... -那个渔夫说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}-Aang... -The fisherman was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我背弃了这个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I did turn my back on the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你对自己太苛求了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You're being too hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你当初的出走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Even if you did run away,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这也许是天意吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I think it was meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你当初留下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}If you had stayed, you would have been killed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可能像其他的气宗人一样被杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}along with all the other airbenders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这是天意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I know it's meant to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,天下人现在需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The world needs you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你给人们带来了希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You give people hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,当祖寇殿下看到他的对手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}When Prince Zuko saw that it was his father
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然是他的父王时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}who had come to duel him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他向他乞求宽恕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}he begged for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,父王,求您了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Please, father,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是心系火烈国安危\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I only had the Fire Nation's best interests at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉我出言不逊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm sorry I spoke out of turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你得为你的荣誉而战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You will fight for your honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我无意冒犯您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I meant you no disrespect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是您最忠心的王儿啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I am your loyal son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来较量吧,祖寇王儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Rise and fight, Prince Zuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会与您较量的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I won't fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要学会如何尊敬人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You will learn respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦将会是你最好的老师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}and suffering will be your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我把脸转开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I looked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!!!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aaaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为祖寇殿下是在训练中意外弄伤的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I always thought that Prince Zuko was in a training accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有什么意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}It was no accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,决斗之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}After the duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,国王陛下下令由于祖寇拒绝比武\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}the Fire Lord said that by refusing to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他表现出的是令人羞愧的软弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Zuko had shown shameful weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,作为惩罚他将被驱逐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}As punishment, he was banished,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,并派他去追捕降世神通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}and sent to capture the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只有抓住神通,那时他才可以荣归故里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Only then could he return with his honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他才如此专注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}So that's why he's so obsessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住神通是他重返正常生活的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Capturing the Avatar is the only chance he has
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一途径\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}of things returning to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,然而他的人生再也不会恢复正常了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Things will never return to normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不过重要的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}but the important thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,神通的出现给祖寇带来了希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}the Avatar gives Zuko hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊,救命啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Help! Oh, please, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了,你现在安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}It's okay. You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但我丈夫还很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}But my husband isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,您此言怎讲?索卡还没回来吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}What do you mean? Where's Sokka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在都还没回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}They haven't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们早就应该回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}They should have been back by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这暴风雨就快变成台风了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}And this storm is becoming a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定被困在海上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}They're caught out at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm going to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也跟你一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我就留在这儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证,我们会很快回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We'll be back soon. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哪儿受损了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Where were we hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看呐!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,舵手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The helmsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在哪啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊,阿柏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Come on, Appa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看呐,船在那儿呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The boat! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,降世神通!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}The Avatar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,殿下,请您下令吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}What do you want to do, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,随他去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们得保住这艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}We need to get this ship to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那就向风暴之眼前进吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Then we must head directly into the eye of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我还年轻,我不想死啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm too young to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不年轻了,但我也不想死啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm not, but I still don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住绳子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Hang on to the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哇!哇!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,皇叔,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Uncle, I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Your apology is accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了,你还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Oh! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你欠这个男孩子一个道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}You owe this boy an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他用不着道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}He doesn't have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不如,我白给他条鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}What if, instead of an apology,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就当是我道歉了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I give him a free fish, and we call it even?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上,我不吃肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Actually, I don't eat meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼肉可不算肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Fish ain't meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的,你还没付我工钱呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Seriously, you're still gonna pay me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,卡塔拉,我想你之前说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Katara, I think you were right before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再沉溺于过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm done dwelling on the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我之前没有出走的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I can't make guesses about how things would have turned out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全无法想象事情该如何发展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}If I hadn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我回来了,我就应该担起责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I'm here now, and I'm going to make the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你再也不会做那些噩梦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}I don't think you're gonna have those nightmares anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有你在这里的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}If you weren't here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我可能就死在风暴里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Well, I guess, I wouldn't be either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,神通,多谢你的救命之恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Thank you for saving my life, Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你们听到了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.42,0:23:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,雨停下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}It stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,阿柏!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs45\b0}Uh! Appa!
